Maintainer: Marcus Lehr <marcus.j.lehr@gmail.com>
Description: Import, export, and data manipulation functions for REDCap databases via API. REDCap is a secure web application for building and managing online surveys and databases (<https://projectredcap.org>). It is specifically geared to support online and offline data capture for research studies and operations.
